episodes.title: This Cult Is In Your Area
episodes.description:
What would you do if I told you this cult operates in your area? Because realistically it does. 

Follow along as we discover the truth behind a cult that spreads flyers throughout our country, only to find out they are everywhere and have registered members in practically every country. 

And as you are used to by now, we of course seek some of them out for a face to face chat.
